title: Macau Unemployed Persons
description: The number of unemployed persons in Macau increased to 15.20 Thousand in the third quarter of 2022 from 13.90 Thousand in the second quarter of 2022. Unemployed Persons in Macau averaged 9.85 Thousand from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 15.20 Thousand in the third quarter of 2022 and a record low of 6 Thousand in the first quarter of 1997. In Macau, unemployed persons are individuals who are without a job and actively seeking to work. This page provides - Macao Unemployed Persons - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics and Census Service, Government of Macao SAR
